        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1898",
        "content": "He gave them a little whip, saying, 'Whip and slash with this, and as much money as you want will jump up before you.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
